Math.max(x,y)	Math.min(x,y)	Math.min(x,y)	Math.abs(x)
int randomNum = (int)(Math.random() * 101);  // 0 to 100
Define an If statement
if (condition) { /run code here/ } 
Else
}else{ /run else code here/ }
Loops		break (jumps out of loop)  continue (ends iteration)
While loop -  while (condition) { /run code here/ }
While loop -  for (A start; B end; C increment) { /run code here/ }
Example for (int i = 0; i <= 10; i = i + 2) { /run code here/ }

